DESCRIPTION:Two Hearts\, One Canvas A Valentine’s Day Adult \\+ Child Art W
	orkshop February 14th\, 10:00 am – noon Ages 5 plus One canvas per adult/c
	hild pair $55 Grab your favorite grown-up and come paint Valentine’s Day t
	ogether! In this sweet and playful workshop\, each adult-and-child duo wil
	l create one shared painting—two hearts\, two personalities\, and one beau
	tiful canvas. You’ll paint side-by-side\, choosing colors\, patterns\, and
	 textures that reflect you\, then blend your ideas together into a keepsak
	e filled with love. There’s no “right way” to paint here. We’ll guide you 
	step-by-step\, but the magic happens in the moments you share—laughing\, e
	xperimenting\, and creating something meaningful as a team.\n\nFrom SEAtod
	ay - Arts & Culture
